social_posts.post_text:
i’ve had this just sitting in my camera roll for over a month, and i’ve just struggled to be motivated to even post it.

i want to keep this short, and avoid over sharing, but lately my mental health has been a bit of a roller coaster. i’ve become a recluse, hardly leaving the house, rarely getting on the board, i just haven’t been motivated to do much of anything.

there’s not much point in bringing this up, i’ve just had a couple people reaching out and checking up on me, and i appreciate those people for that.

take care of yourself.

Video description - Colton rides down a large roll in ramp, then does a frontside 50-50 on a metal funbox ledge.

hi, been a while

Video description - While trying a frontside 50-50 on a bank to ledge, Colton slips off the ledge, and catches himself with his arm fully extended, causing an injury. He tries again and lands the trick.

tags:

#skate #blind #blindskater #visuallyimpaired #stargardts #emo #screamo

2022 was a rollercoaster of a year, but overall, i’ve had some of the best moments of my life, met some of my favorite people in the world, and made so many amazing memories that i’ll hold onto for the rest of my life. thank you to everyone who’s been a part of it in any capacity. love you guys, can’t wait to see what 2023 brings. 🖤

Video description - Las Vegas part:
A view of Las Vegas from the top of the Stratosphere Tower.
Colton drops in on a reservoir bank, and rides off the edge of a wall.
Frontside 50-50 180 out down a hubba.
Frontside 180 down an extended 3 stair at Craig Ranch.
Back in Pennsylvania: 
Colton does a frontside 50-50 on a chunky ledge on top of a bank of a ditch.
A clip from @lizdeliseband’s set opening for Algernon Cadwallader.
Colton does a Muska Flip up a kicker.
Frontside 50-50 180 out on a bank to ledge.
Indy grab over a kicker to kicker gap, comes back and does a kickflip off the side of the kicker.
A clip from @ojneband’s set from a house show with Frail Body.
Kickflip over an A-frame, then Frontside 50-50 down the A-frame hubba.
Indy grab up a kicker over a tall trash can.
Kickflip out of a kicker over a trash can laying on its side.

Michigan Part:
@shannebrigham and @liquidcanes open the front door of the AirBnB to find a giant inflatable deer named Gerald standing in the living room staring at them.
Colton ollie’s an extended 4 stair at Ann Arbor.
Frontside 50-50 down an extended 4 stair hubba.
A clip of @nicholasmullinss watching @asfvision and and @shannebrigham sing a song about him in @danthemancina’s backyard. 
At @modernskate, Colton manuals a ledge on top of a pyramid.
Launching out of a ramp, Colton does a frontside 50-50 on the entire fun box hubba.

A clip of Colton in a wall of death at @alphawolfcvlt’s set at @blueridgerockfest.

Back in Pennsylvania:
Colton does a frontside 50-50 on an out ledge to drop.
While trying to manual the same out ledge to drop, Colton take a bad slam, tries again, and lands the manual.

A clip from @oolong.li’s set at DIY Super Bowl.

On @justinthebishop’s backyard half pipe, Colton does a kickflip fakie.
